data.name: introduction.Text
data.value:
Hello and welcome to the WoW section of the AIO Game Assistant application! This application is an game assistant which will allow you do many things such as browse auction house sales, character profiles etc, there are going to be many more tools integrated into the project however at this current time there is only the WoW character profile, please note that this is still in very, very, very early alpha.
Thank you for your support and development.
~The Team
PS: To begin simply click one of the buttons on the side panel (Only one working at the current time is the "Character Profile")
